  title: 'French Stream - Ontario PNP | Immigratic',
  description: 'French Stream under Ontario Immigrant Nominee Program (OINP). Express Entry based pathway with +600 CRS points for French-speaking professionals. Coming soon - comprehensive assessment tools.',
  keywords: 'French Stream, Ontario PNP, OINP, Express Entry, CRS points, French-speaking, Ontario immigration, permanent residence',
