          Stream
        </span>
      </h1>

      <!-- Subtitle -->
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-indigo-100 max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-12 opacity-0 animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.6s; animation-fill-mode: forwards;">
        Ontario Immigrant Nominee Program (OINP) - Express Entry Based
        <br class="hidden md:block">
        <span class="text-yellow-300">+600 CRS points boost for French-speaking professionals</span> in the Express Entry pool.
      </p>

      <!-- Program Icon -->
      <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500/20 to-purple-500/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-12 opacity-0 animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.8s; animation-fill-mode: forwards;">
        <span class="text-6xl">üá´üá∑</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Coming Soon Message -->
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto opacity-0 animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 1s; animation-fill-mode: forwards;">
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-2xl border border-white/20 p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">üöß Under Development</h2>
          <p class="text-indigo-100 mb-6">
            We're working hard to bring you a comprehensive French Stream assessment tool.
            This program will include:
          </p>
          <ul class="text-left text-indigo-100 space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-indigo-400">‚úÖ</span>
              <span>Express Entry pool eligibility verification</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-indigo-400">‚úÖ</span>
